The following commands will generate a summary of the contents of the SBOM to the console.

```bash
sbom2doc --input flask.spdx 

│ SBOM Summary │
╰──────────────╯
┏━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┓
